{"tid":599700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三萬蚊過夜呀 你個黨係雞黎架！","createTime":"2018-03-20T15:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T16:27:59.000Z","uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0425fcab06313efc05036e026be3cbc819405d2","tid":599700,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T15:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/20/234904_1326b199c95e327be3be6b97392d9de3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F20%2F234904_1326b199c95e327be3be6b97392d9de3.png&h=085be3ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n民主黨今晚舉行二十三週年黨慶，特首林鄭月娥傍晚在多數問責官員出席過酒會後約七時三十分到場，主席胡志偉連同張文光、林卓廷親自在會場正門外迎接。平日常穿旗袍的林鄭，今次身穿桃紅色旗袍，上配搭白色外衣，配合喜慶氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭今次打破特首少有參與晚宴的做法，坐在主家席，與黨主席胡志偉相鄰而坐期間他不時另一來賓，海洋公園前主席盛智文交投接耳。即使立法會將要辯論《財政預算案》，議員都暫時不談政事，盡情談天說地。<br />\n<br />\n今次晚宴的重點環節，還是進行募捐籌款。在李華明全力勸捐，並獲點唱《笑看風雲》一曲時，在台下觀賞的林鄭即填寫表格登記認捐三萬元，成為首名捐款予民主黨的現任特首。<br />\n<br />\n然而，林鄭逗留至晚上八時五十分即行離去，記者問到今次是否「大和解」的表現，她並沒有回應。<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180320/577668\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180320%2F577668&d=%2BALUWLL8g8vg%2BemGNebYc0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=cac2e467\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180320%2F577668&h=57ed04c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180320/577668</a>"},{"pid":"0e7a9aa2a78c61cbb4615ca7502232cf234cb156","tid":599700,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf906ed690943cd42557022dcf96ac928f49198","tid":599700,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T16:27:59.000Z","msg":"有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}